# Advanced Product Search API — quick request runner
#
# A plain-text alternative to the Postman collection, for the "REST Client"
# VS Code extension or a JetBrains IDE: click "Send Request" above any block and
# the response opens beside it. No import step.
#
# Switch target by editing @baseUrl below — the deployed service, or a local
# instance. Note the API rate-limits each client to 60 /search per minute, so
# clicking Send rapidly starts returning 429; that is the limiter working, and
# every response carries RateLimit-* headers showing the remaining budget
# (see request 15).

@baseUrl = https://advanced-search-api-chet.onrender.com
# @baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### 1. Service Index
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### 2. Search — Basic (q=drill)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=drill

### 3. Search — Filters + Facets
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=drill&category=Tools&minPrice=50&maxPrice=500&sort=relevance&order=desc&page=1&pageSize=10

### 4. Search — Browse Mode (by popularity)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?sort=popularity&order=desc&pageSize=5

### 5. Search — Exclude-own-dimension facet
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?category=Tools

### 6. Search — Typo (low-recall suggestions)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=driil

### 7. Search — Subcategories (ANY-of)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?subcategory=Drills&subcategory=Power%20Tools

### 8. Search — By Location
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?location=Berlin

### 9. Search — Sort by created_at
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?sort=created_at&order=desc&pageSize=5

### 10. Search — Pagination (page 2)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?page=2&pageSize=10

### 11. Search — Validation Error (400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=drill&pageSize=500

### 12. Autocomplete (q=cord)
GET {{baseUrl}}/autocomplete?q=cord&limit=5

### 13. Suggest — Did You Mean (q=driil)
GET {{baseUrl}}/suggest?q=driil

### 14. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 15. Search — Rate limit (inspect headers, or trip the 429)
# Look at the response headers: RateLimit-Limit / RateLimit-Remaining / RateLimit-Reset.
# Send this ~61 times within a minute (or lower RATE_LIMIT_SEARCH locally) and it
# flips to 429 with a typed body and a Retry-After header. GET /health is exempt.
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=drill
